ISLAMABAD, Mar 21 (APP): Secretary General of Organization of Islamic Cooperation (OIC) Hissein Brahim Taha arrived here on Monday to attend 48th session of the OIC Council of Foreign Ministers.
He was warmly welcomed by Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib, Special Representative on Religious Harmony Muhammad Tahir Ashrafi and officials of Ministry of Foreign Affairs at Airport.
